OL,3,CPost Office confirms 115 branches to
OL,4,Cclose, with 1,000 workers at risk
OL,6,FThe company published a full list of
OL,7,Fbranches which are set to close across
OL,8,Fthe UK. ITV News reporter Cari Davies
OL,9,Freports
OL,11,FThe Post Office has announced that
OL,12,Fmore than 100 of its branches are
OL,13,Fclosing as part of a
OL,14,F"transformational" plan to fix its
OL,15,Ffinances.
