OL,3,CPost Office confirms 115 branches to
OL,4,Cclose, with 1,000 workers at risk
OL,6,FThe changes, which aim to boost
OL,7,Fpostmaster pay by #250 million over
OL,8,Ffive years, were confirmed by the
OL,9,Fgroup's chairman Nigel Railton on
OL,10,FWednesday morning.
OL,12,FHe said the shake-up will also offer a
OL,13,F"new deal for postmasters" by
OL,14,Fincreasing their share of revenue and
OL,15,Fgiving them a greater say in the
OL,16,Frunning of the business.
