OL,3,CPost Office confirms 115 branches to
OL,4,Cclose, with 1,000 workers at risk
OL,6,FThe Post Office has 11,500 branches
OL,7,Facross the UK, including 115 Crown
OL,8,FPost Offices found in city centres,
OL,9,Fwhich are staffed by Post Office
OL,10,Femployees.
OL,12,FSome 2,000 are operated by the
OL,13,Forganisation's partners, such as Tesco
OL,14,Fand WHSmith. Independent postmasters
OL,15,Foperate the remaining 9,000 as
OL,16,Ffranchises.
