OL,3,CPost Office confirms 115 branches to
OL,4,Cclose, with 1,000 workers at risk
OL,6,FThe plans, which are subject to
OL,7,Fgovernment funding, would see average
OL,8,Fbranch pay doubled by 2030, with #120
OL,9,Fmillion in additional pay by the end
OL,10,Fof the first year.
OL,12,FThe announcement follows a turbulent
OL,13,Fyear for the Post Office. The business
OL,14,Fand its former management have been
OL,15,Fsubject to an inquiry about how faulty
OL,16,Faccounting software led to hundreds of
OL,17,Fsubpostmasters being wrongfully
OL,18,Fconvicted.
