OL,3,CPost Office confirms 115 branches to
OL,4,Cclose, with 1,000 workers at risk
OL,6,FThe scandal saw the defective Horizon
OL,7,Fsystem give the impression money was
OL,8,Fmissing from their branches, leading
OL,9,Fto some being sent to prison.
OL,11,FMr Railton said: "The Post Office has
OL,12,Fa 360-year history of public service
OL,13,Fand today we want to secure that
OL,14,Fservice for the future by learning
OL,15,Ffrom past mistakes and moving forward
OL,16,Ffor the benefit of all postmasters.
